title: Jack Van Impe - A Socalist America (VIDEO)
description:
Ronald Regan said there are only two places where socialism will work - heaven, where they don't need it and hell where they already have it.

For the USA to be following in the footsteps of the USSR and communist China is unthinkable to most, but the evidence shows that we are moving inexorably toward socialism...

And this is the fulfillment of Bible prophecy!

Prophecy experts Drs. Jack and Rexella Van Impe show you:

-What socialism is
-How America is being moved toward it
-What the results will be
-Where this is predicted in Scripture
-How you can defend yourself, your family and your nation
-And much more!
